      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i've been having such a hard time sleeping lately like im tossing and turning all night. i already take a bit of melatonin every night but it isnt really doing much anymore. my doctor recently prescribed me some zolpidem (ambien) for when things get really bad. i was thinking of just taking both at the same time tonight to see if it helps me knock out better? is that okay to do?",
