    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i totally get that, but i've heard they actually work pretty well together because melatonin helps with the cycle and the ambien just knocks you out. my doctor didn't really say anything about the melatonin since it's just an over the counter supplement, so i assumed it was fine. won't it just be a bit more effective? i'm just so exhausted i really need something to work tonight.",
